<refsect1 xml:id="_description">
<title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<simpara><emphasis>abrt-bodhi</emphasis> is the command-line tool for listing a new updates. Bodhi can be
queried by release, bug id or package name.</simpara>
</refsect1>
